{"tid":2498773,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"烏蠅定曱甴污糟啲？","createTime":"2021-04-21T11:30:55.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-21T11:38:19.000Z","uid":96854,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"51eb6f550d36031810d3f8b1d91000fd5fb05f9b","tid":2498773,"uid":96854,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T11:30:55.000Z","msg":"烏蠅曱甴｜烏蠅比曱甴污糟兩倍 醫生話你知食咗烏蠅曱甴飯後果有幾嚴重<br />\n <a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/lifestyle/20210421/TOIX7TQVORAQ7KSKXCYPNHNQIE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2F20210421%2FTOIX7TQVORAQ7KSKXCYPNHNQIE%2F&d=Hmcjt6vcQR8GyvD5m8y4dMRCHeky4xD%2FQbA%2BfbsvJuc%3D&h=43e3e894\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2F20210421%2FTOIX7TQVORAQ7KSKXCYPNHNQIE%2F&h=c2a49caf\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/lifestyle/20210421/TOIX7TQVORAQ7KSKXCYPNHNQIE/</a><br />\n<br />\n試想像看見一隻曱甴在枱底爬來爬去，我想大家會先尖叫，後逃跑，更不用說吃飯了。可是若只是有隻烏蠅在你的食物上盤旋， 你大概揮揮手便會繼續吃。外國媒體曾做過一個有趣調查，發現有67%受訪者會繼續吃被烏蠅沾過的食物，但僅得3%的人會繼續吃曱甴爬過的食物。那是因為烏蠅體積較小，大家覺得牠的殺傷力較低，便忽視了牠，但其實烏蠅比蟑螂骯髒2倍，而且更毒更易致病。 (節錄)"},{"pid":"27184b6ddeff6d4f8447b59539c3b82d7232830a","tid":2498773,"uid":39780,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T11:32:49.000Z","msg":"曱甴爬過都有3%<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0456f8fdc9a262b66aa59b1b66d263c8e577e80a","tid":2498773,"uid":96854,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"27184b6ddeff6d4f8447b59539c3b82d7232830a","tid":2498773,"uid":39780,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T11:32:49.000Z","msg":"曱甴爬過都有3%<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T11:38:19.000Z","msg":"爬過仲敢食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}